{"type": "article", "id": 8094, "title": "JRDN 4 X PS4 运动鞋", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-03T07:42:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234742OoZ0m4jIhebcaByu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tFreakersneaks 最近推出了最新的白色款 JRDN 4 X PS4 运动鞋，把 Sony 最新的 Playstation 4 和Nike 经典 JS 相结合。与此前发布的黑色款相似的是，鞋跟后面也有一个定制的 HDMI 数据线和接入口，不过他们都没什么用，纯粹是为了好看和彰显特色，让鞋子看起来有种浓浓的“科技感”。<a href=\"http://freakersneaks.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是官方网站</a>，可以查看购买信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234740wQjyv3xOez98m1Dc.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234741mBpgEtxK5au6oTq4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234741XR3hLzfUspIxyYod.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65525672\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052347416eyDtVnpYrBT3GzL.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}